="1900_AS_RBH_3_00003"/>Alt-Aussee</placeName><date>4 8 00</date></stamp></physDesc></msDesc></witness></listWit><listBibl><biblStruct corresp="ASBH"><monogr><author ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</author><author ref="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</author><title level="m">Briefwechsel 1891–1931</title><editor>Hg. Konstanze Fliedl</editor><imprint><pubPlace>Wien, Zürich</pubPlace><publisher>Europaverlag</publisher><date when="1992">1992</date></imprint><biblScope unit="pp">149–151</biblScope></monogr></biblStruct></listBibl></sourceDesc></fileDesc><profileDesc><langUsage><language ident="de-AT">German</language></langUsage><correspDesc><correspAction type="sent"><persName ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler, Arthur</persName><placeName ref="#pmb213">Bad Ischl</placeName><date when="1900-08-03" n="01">3. 8. 1900</date></correspAction><correspAction type="received"><persName ref="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</persName><placeName ref="#pmb34401">Altaussee</placeName></correspAction><correspContext><tei:ref type="belongsToCorrespondence" target="#pmb10863">Beer-Hofmann, Richard</tei:ref><ref subtype="previous_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1900-08-02_01">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, 2. 8. 1900</ref><ref subtype="next_letter" type="withinCorrespondence" target="1900-08-03_02">Beer-Hofmann an Schnitzler, 3. 8. 1900</ref></correspContext></correspDesc></profileDesc><encodingDesc><refsDecl><ab>References to Arthur Schnitzler’s diary online consist of the relevant dates only, 
